# S07-T04: Unit Tests

## Objective
Cover pure modules: binary codec, normalization, ring buffer, performance manager.

## Acceptance Criteria
- `src/services/telemetry/protocol/__tests__/v1.test.ts` — encode/decode round-trip.
- `src/features/telemetry/__tests__/normalize.test.ts` — unit conversions + clamping.
- `src/shared/util/__tests__/RingBuffer.test.ts` — push/at/wraparound.
- `src/services/__tests__/PerformanceManager.test.ts` — FPS state transitions.

## Steps
1. Author tests per module.
2. Add corpus of telemetry fixtures (binary blobs).
3. Ensure pure-module isolation (no DOM imports).
4. Wire into `pnpm test`.

## Invariants
- No I/O, no timers in unit tests (use `vi.useFakeTimers`).
- One concern per test file.
- Behavioral assertions only (no snapshots).
